The paper discusses a methodology for optimizing machine learning pipelines for image classification, which falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of optimization techniques such as grid search, random search, and Bayesian optimization, which fall under the category of data science (cs.DS) and neural networks (cs.NE).
